'''210型核潜艇'''，[[俄国|俄国]]称为'''AS-12'''，英语世界多称为“'''Losharik'''”（{{lang-ru|Лошарик}}，来自于马loshad和球体sharik的[[混合词|混合词]]）号潜艇。它有核反应堆，设计上有着独特的多球形壓力殼构造<ref name=rs20030820/>。据信能潜到6000米深度<ref name=multiplate2>{{cite web |url=http://flot.com/news/other/sarov.htm |title=ГРУ контролирует морские глубины |author=Владимир Иванов |date=2008-10-03 |publisher=nvo.ng.ru |accessdate=2013-03-10 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6F33M8cVO?url=http://flot.com/news/other/sarov.htm |archivedate=2013-03-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。该艇于1988年铺龙骨，由于缺少资金，延至2003年8月下水，它主要使命是科研和特种任务。<ref name=rs20030820/>

它的名称可能来源于多层的球体外壳，另外也取自一个俄国卡通形象，一匹用球体组成的的玩具马。<ref name=rs20030820>{{cite web |url=http://www.inauka.ru/fact/article34528.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-09-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090306035926/http://www.inauka.ru/fact/article34528.html |archivedate=2009-03-06 }} {{ru icon}}</ref><ref>[http://shipbuilding.ru/eng/news/2003/08/20/losharik/ Project Losharik: Unique, top secret nuclear submarine has been put in the water] {{Wayback|url=http://shipbuilding.ru/eng/news/2003/08/20/losharik/ |date=20210125010728 }}, ''Russian Shipbuilding'', August 20, 2003</ref>

==2019年火灾事故==
2019年7月1日，210型潜艇在俄罗斯海域进行水下海床测量工作时发生火灾。14名船员因吸入有害气体死亡。<ref name=mt>{{cite news |title=14 Russian Sailors Killed in Fire on Nuclear Sub — Reports |url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2019/07/02/14-russian-sailors-killed-in-fire-on-nuclear-sub-reports-a66257 |accessdate=2 July 2019 |work=The Moscow Times |date=2 July 2019 |language=en |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412025908/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2019/07/02/14-russian-sailors-killed-in-fire-on-nuclear-sub-reports-a66257 }}</ref>其中7人为军官，另有2人曾获颁[[俄罗斯联邦英雄|俄罗斯联邦英雄]]奖章，后者是俄罗斯国民可以获得最高级别的荣誉头衔。<ref name=bbc_2_July_2019>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-48844013 |title=Russia: Fire kills 14 sailors aboard navy research submersible |publisher=BBC |date=2 July 2019 |accessdate=2 July 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107234009/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-48844013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>火灾发生在当地时间晚上八点半，之后被其他幸存船员扑灭。<ref name=mt/><ref name=usni>{{cite news |title=14 Sailors Die on Secretive Russian Nuclear Submarine - USNI News |url=https://news.usni.org/2019/07/02/14-sailors-die-on-secretive-russian-nuclear-submarine |accessdate=2 July 2019 |work=United States Naval Institute News |date=2 July 2019 |archive-date=2019-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117215252/https://news.usni.org/2019/07/02/14-sailors-die-on-secretive-russian-nuclear-submarine |dead-url=no }}</ref>随后潜艇被拖往位于[[北莫爾斯克|北莫爾斯克]]的[[北方舰队|北方舰队]]基地。<ref name=usni/>

这起事故是继2008年11月9日，[[海豹号核潜艇|海豹号核潜艇]]在日本海发生气体泄漏事故，造成20死21人受伤后，俄罗斯海军发生的最严重的事故。<ref name=mt/>海军总司令负责组织对这起事故的原因展开调查。<ref>{{cite news |title=Underwater vessel fire kills 14 Russian sailors |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-48844013 |accessdate=2 July 2019 |date=2 July 2019 |archive-date=2019-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702181731/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-48844013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

